title: David Blaine Do Not Attempt
overview: David Blaine Do Not Attempt follows world-renowned magician and endurance artist David Blaine exploring the world through the lens of magic. David Blaine takes us on a fascinating cultural exchange and a jaw-dropping journey through extraordinary cultures, where he meets with performers and masters - kindred spirits who inspire and share with him exceptional skills (and secrets) - in Brazil, Southeast Asia, India, the Arctic Circle, South Africa and Japan.
